4:
Y-you there! The beautiful lady with
the long black hair!
7:
Stand back! What is your business
with Lady Phiria?
10: M-my apologies! I mean no harm!
11:
You're the sprite user who fought
during the incident the other day,
correct?
13: Please help us! I beg of you!
20:
A performance troupe? Why would
you need Lady Phiria's help?
23:
We do have a sprite user in our
troupe, but they were injured in
rehearsal...
24:
We told them to rest, but they're
insisting on performing unless we
can find a replacement!
27:
Ah, you're in a real bind then... There
aren't exactly a ton of sprite users in
Palpebra.
34:
No, the ones that do exist rarely
leave the countryside.
35:
But you should know that, right? You
came from outside Palpebra too,
don't you?
38:
So you would like to ask Phiria to be
that replacement, correct? When is
the show?
44:
I don't know much about
performing, but I'm guessing it's not
something you can pick up that
quickly.
48:
Indeed... A performance is quite
different from combat...
51:
W-we will prepare a simple routine
for her!
52:
Please, I beg of you! If we don't find a
replacement, our sprite user will end
up hurting themselves!
55: Um... I'd like to give performing a try.
59:
Are you sure? You do realize this will
involve showing off your powers,
correct?
65:
I want to use this power to help
others. Besides...
68: This is to help people smile, right?
76:
B-but... Performing carries its own
set of dangers! What's moreâ€”
80:
Come on, it'll be fine. Besides, she
wants to do it, and that's what's
important.
82:
If you're too overprotective, she'll
end up rebelling, you know? Do you
want another Arum running around?
87:
Please let me do this! I'll work really
hard!
98:
Oh dear, oh dear, oh dear! I-I'm so
very sorry!
105:
I suppose this provides an
opportunity for her to practice
controlling her output...
108:
However, at this rate, even the
golem made by the Academy isn't
going to stand a chance against her.
116:
Arum! I told you not to bother Phiria
during practice, didn't I?
119:
Hehe, it's fine. I'm happy to see you
all.
124:
I see rehearsal is going... not well.
Are you having troubles, my lady?
128:
Yes... I've memorized the routine, but
I can't seem to release the correct
amount of power...
134: Did you do all this, Phiria? Cooool!
136: Can I make things go boom too?
140:
What? Of course not. Now come
here, we don't want to bother Phiria
during practice.
145: Nooo! I wanna go boom too!
149:
Um... Could Arum practice with me
for a moment?
154:
Come on, you don't have to do that...
She's just throwing a tantrum.
157:
I-I was just thinking it might be good
for me to take a break and cut loose
a bit. It might help me focus.
160:
I don't see anything wrong with it. As
long as it's just one scarecrow...
164:
Yippee! Come to me, Shadow
Chariot!
168: All right, Arum, just do as I do.
183: Ahaha! You can keep going, right?
198:
Who would've thought the troupe
would let them have a combat
demonstration...
203: You can do it, Lady Phiria!
208: That's it, Arum! Nice and steady!
218: Yeah! This is so much fun!
